<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><b><span
style='font-size:16.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>中華科技大學教師服務評鑑施行細則</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=right style='text-align:right;layout-grid-mode:char'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>94年2月15日校務會議通過</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=right style='margin-right:5.0pt;text-align:right;
layout-grid-mode:char'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
標楷體'>96年2月5日校務會議通過</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>一、中華科技大學（以下簡稱本校）為提升教師服務之效能，依據本校教師教學服務研究評量辦法訂定服務評鑑施行細則（以下簡稱本細則）。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>二、本細則以計分之方式進行評量，基本分數為七十分，最高分數為一百分。評量範圍及標準包含下列事項：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:18.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>（一）兼任校內行政職務</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:54.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>兼任校內一級主管職務每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>15</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>20</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:54.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>兼任校內二級主管職務每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>5</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>10</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:18.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>（二）招生事務之參與</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:54.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>協助推廣教育招生開班成功者，每班次加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，學生</span><span lang=EN-US>20</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>人以上再加</span><span lang=EN-US>1 </span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:54.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>協助系所招生事宜，依參與程度酌加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1~2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:18.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>（三）校內事務之參與</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任導師，每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，系（科）主任酌加</span><span
lang=EN-US>0~2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。經學務處處務會</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>議依表現及導師遴選辦法有關導師考核事項評定之，每學年酌加</span><span
lang=EN-US>0</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>6</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分</span><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp; </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>或酌減</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>2</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任校級委員會委員且為義務性者，每委員每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，擔任召集人</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>加</span><span
lang=EN-US>2 </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，每學年未出席委員會達兩次以上（含）者，不予加分（因有課</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>或公假除外）。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任系級委員會委員及其召集人、實驗室管理等，且為義務性者，每項加</span><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp; </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，其加分上限為</span><span
lang=EN-US>5</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任校內學術期刊之編輯，每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>3</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任社團（含系學會）指導老師，每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 6.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任校代表隊指導老師，每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>3</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 7.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>承辦系科申請教育部專案，經學校甄選通過者，每案加</span><span
lang=EN-US>2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 8.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>未出席全校性會議（以年度行事曆及會議通知單為準），若無正當理由或</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>事先請假者，每次扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。請假（因公、婚、產、喪假除外）三次以上（含），</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>每次扣</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; 9.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任學輔中心輔導老師每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，學輔中心義務輔導老師加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp; 10.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任第四目至第六目指導老師，帶領學生參加校外競賽加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，並依區域</span><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>性層級及獲得獎項酌加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>10</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分（評量細項於評分標準另訂之）。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:18.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>（四）校外專業服務（加分上限</span><span
lang=EN-US>10</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分）</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>主辦對外學術會議、講習會、研討會者，每次加</span><span
lang=EN-US>3</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任校外學術期刊之編輯，每學年加</span><span
lang=EN-US>2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>擔任政府機關專案計畫之顧問或評審，每案加</span><span
lang=EN-US>2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>主持國際會議，每次加</span><span lang=EN-US>2</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>校外學術演講，每次加</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>獲頒專業優良服務獎項者，每項加</span><span
lang=EN-US>2</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:18.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>（五）其他服務事項</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:54.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>其他足以證明有關服務表現優劣事件，經校教評會評定，其加扣分上下限</span><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp; </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:54.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>為</span><span
lang=EN-US>1</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>&#12316;</span><span lang=EN-US>20</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:18.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>三、本細則經校務會議通過後，陳請校長核定後公布實施，修正時亦同。</span></p>
